{"tid":1407121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【港島示威】示威者佔告士打道封紅隧　王宗堯不介意受阻：幾安全","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:48.000Z","uid":3873,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e038e4e2ded6429d8e15ad3a5f729ef92de20bd","tid":1407121,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"source: 紅底01<br />\n香港01記者在告士打道行車路上見到藝人王宗堯，他正駕車經過，座駕亦受示威者堵塞路面影響而被困，他表示已經阻塞了約20分鐘左右。<br />\n不過，他不覺得示威者行為擾民，稱沒有人打車、燒車，亦沒有追打市民，「幾安全」。<br />\n<br />\n對於有市民認為示威者的做法無法達致目的，他表示：「兄弟爬山，大家都做緊自己嘢。在政府唔回應市民的情況下，任何方法都是一種方法。」他又關心周圍正在設置路障的示威者，「（你們）食咗飯未呀？」<br />\n<br />\n我覺得01記者本來係求其搵個司機諗住答話被班手足影響塞咗好耐車，但點知搵錯咗人答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a1288a352548bcd9e66c1e3a5e71543e50210a","tid":1407121,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/360047/%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BD%94%E5%91%8A%E5%A3%AB%E6%89%93%E9%81%93%E5%B0%81%E7%B4%85%E9%9A%A7-%E7%8E%8B%E5%AE%97%E5%A0%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%8B%E6%84%8F%E5%8F%97%E9%98%BB-%E5%B9%BE%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama&amp;fbclid=IwAR0E4NSgYt7y8tFxwsB39Q4hRuSmMghQC_A9Sp7MoOsaD1qJ_0-07fKWBWs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F360047%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BD%2594%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%259A%25A7-%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%258B%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%2598%25BB-%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5